{"id":"12d75693-aae5-48b6-83f8-36f4d86e23db","name":"God Meeting","description":"<p>It's serious.</p><p>Many gods and goddesses are gathered together for the ultimate, the one and only...</p><p>God Meeting!</p><p>That includes you.</p><p>Some are already asleep, a few are shouting over each other and Nebulean has taken his third set of pills today.</p><p>Only the first day out of three, and nothing has been agreed upon.</p><p>Maybe we just let the creatures in the surface world make the rules for us?</p><p>Or maybe you could make the first change.</p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(175, 36, 36);\"><strong>CHARACTERS</strong></span></p><p><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/5OsgID_VNbgEW2dan4Jdr.webp\"></p><p><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/wyGIEZ7XymFW4j2acjgG9.webp\"></p><p><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/HnwZihclQC7dZWIy-w3Vf.webp\"></p><p><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/Xj9So4P1DUv73p4ETsZAX.webp\"></p><p><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/3iTG1o6Bcqm161IwHYz5K.webp\"></p><p><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/7P8QwK8j4THdO5GUIiBPg.webp\"></p><p><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/EZas730pA-0V9DjbP6T1m.webp\"></p><p><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/WVF6v5_Nqxj-k4eJAsqia.webp\"></p><p><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/LmR6av1VcWSqIls09hVG-.webp\"></p><p><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/NyAFdIi-r1GjNBEvQwqPj.webp\"></p><p><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/kFHh5_KqAun0LE9hoxopR.webp\"></p><p><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/6gVsM9r7m5blOo1wbn_4a.webp\"></p><p><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/_2d2l6rVNUnjNVzvNNfLK.webp\"></p><p><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/0-MMFZ59fd7l0Dot6l2Lo.webp\"></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-